:"2017-01-24T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"聽講過關可能要俾錢個關員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以準備定25蚊美金, 等佢唔駛找, 唔會扮晒野唔找錢俾我. 去到Visa on arrival, 足足等左一個鐘. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多人, 逐個嗌名. 佢地d口音又勁, 要好留心聽住. 見到有人俾美金, 收返越南盾, 刻意找少左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ac4a04d5d62714861f3a513d0fb0eca362c1fa3","tid":93753,"uid":65063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聖誕去左胡志明市4日<br />\n搭uber同grab平過的士好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用grab check 價錢, 但次次用親個app都話太繁忙, 冇車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我搭親的士, 個價錢都平過grab check果個價. 我睇正常的, 唔係私的個價."},{"pid":"293e6db1d9bfa0821289fb63746016c1d160451b","tid":93753,"uid":65063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"班機delay, 落機又夜又攰又餓. 最後竟然9衝左去OK 食杯麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係越南既第一餐竟然係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過佢d便利店上層全層係有枱櫈俾你坐低慢慢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n訓醒先係酒店食早餐<br />\n佢話buffet, 原來係個menu 到指你想食咩, 佢先去煮. 所以全部熱辣辣好好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雞絲湯粉:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/003129_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F003129_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=06ebfb64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01abab2a6ebb00a5f2afcc8674002a5011b3b76c","tid":93753,"uid":65063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T16:48:57.000Z","msg":"第一件事就係9衝去報local tour同買巴士飛. <br />\n<br />\n完全唔駛等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩個人報左三個團, 買左兩張長途巴士飛, total 都係港紙3百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 